        <sponsor name-id="W000800">Mr. Welch</sponsor> (for himself, <cosponsor name-id="O000169">Mr. Owens</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="H001068">Mr. Huffman</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was referred to the <committee-name committee-id="HWM00">Committee on Ways and Means</committee-name>
